codes.biscuit.skyblocklib.managers

Class ItemAbilityFile

  • java.lang.Object
    • codes.biscuit.skyblocklib.managers.ItemAbilityFile

  • public class ItemAbilityFile
extends java.lang.Object
    Manages the item abilities file and exposes the possibility to get abilities by name. Create a new instance that loads abilities from the local file and remote repository with fromFileAndRemote().
    The intention behind this is to have a dynamic way of loading abilities, so the remote repository can update the values without needing to release a new version when the abilities change or new ones get introduced in Skyblock.

      • findAbilityByName

        public java.util.Optional<SkyblockItemAbility> findAbilityByName(java.lang.String abilityName)
        Find an ability object by it's name, for example when it gets detected in a chat message. Returns an optional that either holds the ability or is empty if none was found matching the name. Lookup is case-sensitive!
        Parameters:
        abilityName - Name of the ability to find
        Returns:
        Optional that holds the found ability or is empty
